items.title: Random Wiki
items.headline: Open Up the Randomness Package
items.desc: It's 100% random, action packed with humor, pure nonsense, lots o' spam, fun and tons more! Check out the FTF Roleplayer or just mess around! We define random! Check it out, we guarantee you won't get bored! We take absouletely nothing as vandalism! To us, spam is perfect contributing! Why?! BECAUSE WE'RE RANDOM! Drink your random sauce and get your brain removed! You're going to laugh your vocal cords out when you read our clear definitions... of RANDOM!!

items.desc: The Very Random Wiki is about just that. Randomness. Pop by and add some random content to add the randomness to the very random wiki. items.name: Randomness Is Random Wiki
items.title: Randomness Is Random Wiki
items.headline: Be Random At The Randomness Is Random Wiki
items.desc: This is a recycling bin of ideas you can't share on another wiki. Be is canon information or your shippy fanfiction, as long as it isn't offensive, it's welcome here. We highly encourage random roleplays, and characters for said roleplays are welcome here. No matter how small or irrelevant, we welcome creativity!
